{"tid":1702663,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【歲月催人老】湯費頓與「小馬份」合照被肥仔「奈威」寸老","createTime":"2019-11-09T21:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:18:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc857b51c65cccfec4b9e63dcafba953ef61b47","tid":1702663,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:30:59.000Z","msg":"在電影《哈利波特》（Harry Potter）系列飾演「馬份」的32歲英國男星湯費頓（Tom Felton），日前與「小馬份」畫像合照，他還披上斗篷想回到童年，不過他日漸升高的髮線和額頭上的抬頭紋卻出賣了他。湯費頓一臉無奈地留言自嘲：「老化是一個八婆。」照片一出，引來在《哈》片飾演戇直肥仔「奈威」的Matthew Lewis留言：「你是講你自己！」<br />\n「馬份」八月在南非拍戲時，上載與「妙麗」愛瑪屈臣（Emma Watson）的合照，當時愛瑪專程到南非探班，兩人還穿着睡衣玩結他，令粉絲大為震驚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191109/large/1573295066_8088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191109%2Flarge%2F1573295066_8088.jpg&h=557e2232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191109/large/1573295081_dcbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191109%2Flarge%2F1573295081_dcbe.jpg&h=ea4e2ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191109/60248930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191109%2F60248930&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=160e7b27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191109%2F60248930&h=6075a241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191109/60248930</a>"},{"pid":"0eb07a65a9dde25d2a247a6e602a060d21f839af","tid":1702663,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:32:33.000Z","msg":"小時了了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70